---
// ContactCTA.astro - Reusable contact call-to-action component
---

<section class="contact-cta">
  <div class="cta-content">
    <h2>Ready to work together?</h2>
    <p>Let's discuss how I can help with your next project.</p>
    <a href="mailto:jmaisel@example.com" class="cta-button">Get In Touch</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact-cta {
    background-color: #f0f4ff;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .cta-content {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #333;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    background-color: #0066cc;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background-color: #0052a3;
  }
</style>
